prompt:
You are a requirements rewriter.
Rewrite each requirement into clean natural language suitable for UML state diagram generation.

Return ONLY valid JSON with this schema:
{
  "rewritten_requirements": [
    {
      "source_requirement": "string",
      "rewritten_requirement": "The system shall ..."
    }
  ]
}

Rules:
1. Keep exactly the same number of requirements and same order.
2. Do not add new meaning.
3. Each rewritten requirement must start with "The system shall".
4. Keep them concise and implementation-neutral.

Input JSON:
{
  "functional_requirements": [
    {
      "requirement": "Provide a personalized profile for each user",
      "evidence_quote": "Login – provides a personalized profile for each user, to ensure security."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Allow users to personalize their account and change their password",
      "evidence_quote": "Profile changes – each user can personalize their account, and change their password."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Enable clients to post project requests with requirements for BPO organizations",
      "evidence_quote": "Post project request – clients post their request with requirements for BPO organizations to choose from."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Allow BPO organizations to search and respond to client project requests",
      "evidence_quote": "Search project requests – BPO organizations can search and respond to the requests."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Enable transfer of documents required by BPO organizations through the system",
      "evidence_quote": "Upload source documents – the documents required by the BPO organization can be transferred through the system, and the receiver can download them."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Provide progress updates to clients on work being done",
      "evidence_quote": "Check progress – clients should be constantly updated with the progress of the work."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Allow clients to check their product and quote modifications",
      "evidence_quote": "Quality check and testing – the clients can check their product and quote any modifications."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Enable BPO organizations to upload their products/services for further procedure",
      "evidence_quote": "Upload product/service – BPO organization should upload their product/service for the further procedure (payment, shipment, etc.)."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Facilitate payment from clients to BPO organizations at the end of agreements",
      "evidence_quote": "Payment – clients should pay the BPO organization at the end of their agreement."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Enable shipment of products/services to clients",
      "evidence_quote": "Shipment – the product/service should be delivered to the clients."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Allow clients to rate the service provided by BPO organizations",
      "evidence_quote": "Rating – the clients can rate the service provided by the BPO organization"
    }
  ]
}

